<div class="block block-layout-builder block-field-blocknodeplantfield-cooking-notes">
  
    
      <div class="block__content">
      
  <div class="text-content field field--name-field-cooking-notes field--type-text-long field--label-above">
    <h2 class="field__label">Cooking Notes</h2>
              <div class="field__item"><p>Potatoes can be prepared in many ways: boiled, mashed, cut into pieces and roasted, french-fried, scalloped, made into dumplings or pancakes, grated into hash browns, and even brewed as&nbsp;alcoholic&nbsp;beverages.</p><p>Most potato dishes are served hot, but some are first cooked, then served cold, notably potato salad and potato&nbsp;chips.</p></div>
          </div>

    </div>
  </div>


